---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Ravi Chandu"
  description="Learn about my transition from Chartered Accountancy to data analytics and technology."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        From numbers to insights: A journey in data and analytics
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Hello! I'm Ravi Chandu, a data and analytics specialist with a unique blend of financial expertise and technology skills. My journey began in Chartered Accountancy, where I developed a strong foundation in financial analysis, compliance, and business operations. However, I discovered my true passion lies in transforming raw data into actionable insights.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Today, I help organizations unlock the power of their data through Power BI dashboards, SQL optimization, Power Apps automation, and strategic data analysis. I believe that great data visualization and efficient automation can empower better decision-making across all levels of an organization.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Career Transition -->
    <section class="mb-12 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The Transition</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        While pursuing my Chartered Accountancy qualification, I became fascinated with how businesses could leverage data to improve their operations. I started learning SQL, Excel advanced functions, and eventually Power BI. What began as a side interest quickly became my core expertise.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        The accounting background has been invaluable—it taught me to think critically about data quality, accuracy, and compliance. Combined with technical skills in analytics, this positions me uniquely to bridge the gap between business requirements and technical implementation.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Values -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What I'm Passionate About</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 dark:hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            I believe organizations that make decisions based on data consistently outperform those that rely on intuition alone. My goal is to make data accessible and understandable for everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 dark:hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Manual, repetitive tasks are the enemy of productivity. I'm passionate about identifying opportunities to automate processes, freeing teams to focus on higher-value work.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 dark:hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Continuous Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            The field of data analytics is constantly evolving. I'm committed to staying current with new tools, techniques, and best practices to deliver cutting-edge solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 dark:hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Clear Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            The best analysis is worthless if it can't be understood. I prioritize creating clear, compelling visualizations and explanations that resonate with stakeholders at all levels.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills & Tools -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">My Toolkit</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Business Intelligence</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Power BI (Desktop, Service, Premium)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              DAX Language & M Language
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Data Modeling & Star Schema
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Advanced Excel & Power Pivot
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Database & Backend</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              SQL Server, MySQL, PostgreSQL
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Query Optimization & Performance Tuning
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Database Design & Normalization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Data Warehousing Concepts
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Automation & Development</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Power Apps & Power Automate
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              VBA & Excel Macros
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Basic Python for Data Analysis
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Git & Version Control
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Analytics & Statistics</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Statistical Analysis & Hypothesis Testing
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              Forecasting & Trend Analysis
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              KPI Development & Benchmarking
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600 dark:bg-cyan-400"></span>
              A/B Testing & Experimentation
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Beyond Work -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Beyond Work</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        When I'm not analyzing data or building dashboards, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, or sharing knowledge through writing and mentoring. I'm an active participant in data analytics communities and enjoy helping others navigate their transition into the tech world—much like I did.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        I'm always interested in connecting with fellow data enthusiasts, business leaders looking for analytics solutions, and anyone passionate about data-driven decision making.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 dark:from-blue-900 dark:to-cyan-800 text-white mt-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Connect!</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 dark:text-blue-200 mb-8">
        Whether you have a project opportunity or just want to chat about data and analytics,  I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="mailto:ravichandu464@gmail.com"
          class="px-8 py-4 rounded-lg bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Send Email
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com/in/raviram"
          target="_blank"
          class="px-8 py-4 rounded-lg border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
        >
          Connect on LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
